room_title: Escape room "Becoming Houdini" by I-20 Escape in Ruston
room_description: You and your team of researchers have stumbled upon Houdini's dressing room that he was about to use for his final performance. Inside you will uncover some of his highly kept secrets and keys to his haunted past. Rumor has it that his spirit lives on in this very room. You and your team will have 60 minutes to uncover the mysteries of Harry Houdini and escape his traps. However, should you fail, the mysteries may be lost forever...
